parameters:
I feel a sense of peace in the warmth of the bonfire.... My
stamina has fully recovered!

So you've come all the way here. It was quite a task to
prepare the bonfire...

The boss here... isn't it too overpowered?! I don't think
there's anything I can say from my perspective.

\SE[14]... That thing is the cause of her illness. \!\SE[13]
If we eliminate it, we should be able to cure Meria-chan...

\SE[5]I remember... When we fought before, \SE[0]it was
revived and we couldn't defeat it completely...

\SE\SE[16]I see. It seems that exterminating that is
difficult for humans. \!\SE[0]Then I will erase it for you.
\!\SE[16]Hey, will you support me? Laura?

\SE[14]She seems to be full of motivation...! W-Watch
out...! \SE[13]

\SE[16]Ahaha... Even though you were running away... You
have quite the courage, don't you? \SE[60]I'll tear you
apart and erase you from this world...!!
